1.name: Officer
1.description: Commissioned military class responsible for authority and command.

2.name: Engineer
2.description: Imperial engineers are the repairman units for the Empire.

3.name: Medical
3.description: A type of soldier and officer attached to the Galactic Empire's ground and naval forces that has specialized medical training.

4.name: Security
4.description: A law-enforcement and intelligence agency of the Galactic Empire charged with matters of internal state security and ensuring the loyalty of citizens.

5.name: Technician
5.description: Imperial weapons technicians, also known as Imperial gunners, operate turbolasers and ion cannons of capital ships and military bases.

6.name: Stormtrooper
6.description: Stormtroopers serve as frontline assault forces and form the backbone of the Imperial Military.
